      "span_text": "The uninterrupted evolution of AV publications began in 1982 with the work of [CITATION_1] and, from there, it followed an exponential curve (Figure 3 ), the years 2016 and 2017 registering the greatest number of publications of 1,379 and 1,856 papers, respectively."
